# Kin SaaS Environment Variables

## Production Environment Variables (Vercel)

### Frontend (Next.js)
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://kin-saas.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.kin-saas.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_live_YOUR_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY
NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_live_YOUR_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY
NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PRICE_ID=price_YOUR_STRIPE_PRICE_ID
NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=https://your-sentry-dsn.ingest.sentry.io/project-id

### Backend (API)
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_YOUR_CLERK_SECRET_KEY
CLERK_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_YOUR_CLERK_WEBHOOK_SECRET

### Supabase Database
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key

### Stripe Payments
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_YOUR_STRIPE_SECRET_KEY
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_YOUR_STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET
STRIPE_PRICE_ID=price_YOUR_STRIPE_PRICE_ID

### OpenClaw Integration
OPENCLAW_API_KEY=your-openclaw-api-key
OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL=https://your-gateway.openclaw.io

### Bot Integration
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=your-telegram-bot-token
WHATSAPP_API_KEY=your-whatsapp-api-key

### Security
JWT_SECRET=your-jwt-secret-min-32-chars
ENCRYPTION_KEY=your-encryption-key-min-32-chars

### Monitoring
SENTRY_DSN=https://your-sentry-dsn.ingest.sentry.io/project-id
SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN=your-sentry-auth-token
LOG_LEVEL=info

### Rate Limiting
RATE_LIMIT_REQUESTS=100
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=60000

